<br>
Sadly, the very few groups i'v been in that had more than two mercs did extremly poorly (mostly due to low RR).<br>
<br>
It's very depended on others RAs (enemys and friends). I was in a very well balanced group, with random RRed people (highs and lows). We rolled two mid groups like we had three times their numbers. But when we stumbled across 2 savages, a healer and a stealther, we got wtfpwned. Turns out, that little group was like RR7+s or something. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
